<p>The Department of Avionics focuses on creating professional-quality electrical and computational systems for our launch vehicles and ground communications. Avionics’ research and development goals are split between three Divisions:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Stability and Control - Flight software; Active control systems; Control theory; Computer Vision; Recovery systems software; Sensor filtering and fusion</li>
	<li>Communication - Telemetry; Signal processing hardware and software; Antenna design; Vehicle Tracking; Data visualization</li>
	<li>Architecture - physical support structure; circuit fabrication; embedded systems and software; Real-time systems; Fault-tolerant systems</li>
</ul>

